thread.title: BRIEF-Tangelo Games Pre-Announces Q4 Revenue And Provides Operational Update

title: BRIEF-Tangelo Games Pre-Announces Q4 Revenue And Provides Operational Update
text:
February 5, 2018 / 11:07 AM / Updated 2 minutes ago BRIEF-Tangelo Games Pre-Announces Q4 Revenue And Provides Operational Update Reuters Staff 
Feb 5 (Reuters) - Tangelo Games Corp: 
* TANGELO GAMES PRE-ANNOUNCES Q4 REVENUE AND PROVIDES OPERATIONAL UPDATE 
* TANGELO GAMES CORP - Q4 REVENUE CAD $8.8 MILLION, DECLINE OF 5.6% FROM PRIOR YEAR‘S QUARTER​ 
* TANGELO GAMES CORP - ‍ EXPECT TO RELEASE NEW ENGLISH-LANGUAGE MOBILE APP, BEST JACKPOT, BY END OF MARCH 2018​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
